projectGridLines.title: Project 1 Title: Reduce TCP retransmissions, Project 2 Title: Creating pseudo/virtual production setups
projectGridLines.description:
Project 1 Title: Reduce TCP retransmissions


Description: Analyzing cause for TCP retransmission, finding root cause and presenting

solution to reduce them

Skill sets: Networking & C++

Traits expectation: Problem solving, debugging

Expected learning: Deep understanding of networking

Specific courses required for project execution: Networking, C++


Project 2 Title: Creating pseudo/virtual production setups


Description: We have complex trading setups, with multiple components governed by specific

configurations & connected via multiple ways/protocols. We want to mimic exact replica of

these setups required for varied workflows including release testing

Skill sets: C++, networking, DS-Algo

Traits expectation: Problem solving, debugging

Expected learning: Virtualization, networking, Order Manager

Specific courses required for project execution: C++, networking, DS-Algo
